				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p>Ali Matar Contractors Ltd, a culmination of the merger between Head Office &amp; General Construction and General Contractors, has been a prominent presence in the Cyprus, Paphos area for over a decade. Our journey began in 2004 when Mr. Ali Mohamed founded Ali Matar General Construction, which later joined forces with General Contractors to successfully bid on larger-scale projects. Today, we are on the brink of transitioning from a limited company to an unlimited corporation registered in Cyprus, poised for even greater growth and access to investment funds to fuel our expansion.</p><p>With a steadfast commitment to delivering the highest levels of quality construction services at fair and competitive prices, we cater to both small and large-scale projects. Over the years, we have specialized in residential contracting, undertaking construction, repair, alteration, and renovation projects.</p><p>As we look to the future, we&#8217;re gearing up to shift our focus towards larger commercial clients, driven by the flourishing business opportunities in our local area. Our comprehensive business plan outlines our strategic goals and tasks to make this transition seamless and capture a significant share of this competitive industry.</p><p>At Ali Matar Contractors Ltd, our mission revolves around client satisfaction. We achieve this by maintaining the utmost professionalism, integrity, honesty, and fairness in all our relationships, be it with suppliers, subcontractors, professional associates, or customers. Our dedicated team is available 24/7, and we pride ourselves on finding the perfect land for your construction needs while offering adjustments to the original building scheme to accommodate specific client or customer requests.</p><p>Our services encompass a wide spectrum, including general construction, full building from scratch, remodeling, alterations, permitting, site preparations, carpentry, cement foundations, painting, plumbing, utilities installation, swimming pool construction, and full insulation. Furthermore, we are open to subcontracting, collaborating to bring your vision to life.</p><p>Ali Matar Contractors Ltd is committed to shaping a new industry standard, with a vision of excellence and sustainability.</p><p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Our Mission is:</strong></span></p><p>►To perform the highest levels of quality construction services at fair and market competitive prices for our customers.</p><p>►To ensure the longevity of our company through repeat and referral business achieved by customer satisfaction in all areas including; timelines, attention to detail and service-minded attitudes.</p><p>►To maintain the highest levels of professionalism, integrity, honesty and fairness in our relationships with our suppliers, subcontractors, professional associates and customers.</p><p><strong><span style="color: #ff0000;">What We Do:<br /></span></strong></p><p>►Part of our job is to find the area/land to build,</p><p>►We also offer adjustments in the original building scheme for any construction</p><p>►As per client or customer requests.</p><p><span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>Type of Work:</strong></span></p><p>►Villa (1) cost 2 million EUR, VIP client<br />Advantage: Permanent residency, Non-Citizen</p><p>►Villa (2) cost 400 thousand EUR<br />Advantage: Permanent residency, Non-Citizen</p><p>We offer renovation related to construction for all buildings including apartments, offices, shops etc.<strong><span style="color: #ff0000;"><br /></span></strong></p>								</div>
